OL,3,CMark Hughes leaves Carlisle United
OL,5,FCarlisle United have confirmed that
OL,6,FMark Hughes has left his position as
OL,7,FHead Coach by what the club described
OL,8,Fas 'mutual agreement'.
OL,10,FIn an announcement posted on the
OL,11,FBlues' website on Thursday 28 May, the
OL,12,Fclub said it "would like to place on
OL,13,Frecord its sincere thanks to Mark for
OL,14,Fhis professionalism, commitment and
OL,15,Fleadership during his time at Brunton
OL,16,FPark".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
