CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1780218421
OL,3,CMark Hughes leaves Carlisle United
OL,5,FIt continued: "While everyone
OL,6,Fconnected with the club was
OL,7,Fdisappointed not to achieve promotion,
OL,8,FMark played an important role in
OL,9,Fstabilising the team and helping to
OL,10,Fmove the club forward."
OL,12,FHughes was appointed as Carlisle
OL,13,FUnited head coach in September 2025,
OL,14,Fand lost his first game while in
OL,15,Fcharge two days later, when the Blues
OL,16,Flost 2-1 at Grimsby Town.
OL,18,FCarlisle United Chairman Tom Piatak
OL,19,Fsaid: "Mark has conducted himself with
OL,20,Freal professionalism throughout his
OL,21,Ftime at Carlisle United.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
