CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1780218421
OL,3,CMark Hughes leaves Carlisle United
OL,5,F"We are grateful for the work he has
OL,6,Fdone, the standards he brought, and
OL,7,Fthe progress made during the season.
OL,9,F"Following open and respectful
OL,10,Fdiscussions, both parties agreed this
OL,11,Fwas the right time for the club to
OL,12,Fmove in a different direction.
OL,14,F"Mark leaves with our thanks and best
OL,15,Fwishes, and he will always be welcome
OL,16,Fat Brunton Park."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
