OL,3,CMark Hughes leaves Carlisle United
OL,5,FThe club also announced that First
OL,6,FTeam Head Coach Frankie McAvoy will
OL,7,Fleave the club. He too was thanked
OL,8,F"for his service and contribution
OL,9,Fduring his time at Carlisle United."
OL,11,FThe club says further announcements
OL,12,Fregarding the now vacant Head Coach
OL,13,Fposition will be made "in due course".
